{"title":"Remembering","author":{"name":"Yuan Chen"},"publishDate":"2011-03-07","lines":[{"line":"I daydream, melancholy at the windowsill—","stanza":1,"number":1},{"line":"memories I will never tell—","stanza":1,"number":2},{"line":"our passion is the late night hours,","stanza":2,"number":3},{"line":"our tearful goodbyes at dawn.","stanza":2,"number":4},{"line":"Mountains and rivers divide us,","stanza":3,"number":5},{"line":"I’ve given up hoping for rain.","stanza":3,"number":6},{"line":"Divided, I dream of you today—","stanza":4,"number":7},{"line":"I even embrace the pain.","stanza":4,"number":8}]}